data.description: PRICED $30k BELOW APPRAISAL!!  Introducing your dream home! This spacious 3-bedroom single family residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and luxury. Step into a sprawling family room that's perfect for gatherings, and a versatile office/den, ideal for remote work.  Enjoy energy efficiency with a brand new solar-powered roof.   With 2 bathrooms Plus a pool bath, mornings will be a breeze.  Take a dip in the pristine pool, powered by a newer pump, or unwind in the open floorplan with split bedrooms for added privacy. Host dinners in the elegant formal dining room, and retreat to the primary bedroom, complete with French doors opening to the pool, walk-in closets, and a spa-like primary bath featuring dual vanities, a garden tub, and a walk-in shower. Let your pets roam freely in the newly fenced yard with a convenient dog run. NEW ROOF 2023, MICROWAVE 2023, RANGE 2020, WATER HEATER 2022, SOLAR PANELS 2020 (will be paid off at closing), WATER SYSTEM W/REVERSE OSMOSIS 2023, LANAI RESCREEN 2023, FENCE 2022. Ring and Vivint Security System and Cameras included plus NEST Thermostat.  This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, stylel, and functionality – make it yours today and experience the Florida lifestyle at its finest!
